(defun jde-javadoc-insert (*name* &rest *texts*)
  "Insert the template *NAME* or *TEXTS* and a newline.
If *NAME* value is nil *TEXTS* are inserted if non-nil.  If *NAME* and
*TEXTS* are nil the function does nothing.
